{"tid":397782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[童年拎]純粹分享一下童年嘅回憶","createTime":"2017-09-12T17:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T12:21:43.000Z","uid":144430,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5102c5f50fe129e36d55f620d9a7e99baaa753ef","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"「你地啲後生學咩人講懷念阿？」<br />\n童年，人人都擁有 。有人嘅童年充滿歡樂，有人則係投身於學業中。唔知係咪踏入社會後，明白到美好事物背後嘅真相，逐漸就想念昔日嘅動人時光。細路哥時，一出街大家對住嘅並唔係一部部冷血無情的電子毒品，而係會同鄰居打招呼吹吹水。講起鄰居，最大印象係住對面大我約五歲嘅三姐妹。每次老豆媽子唔得閒，佢地就會入黎搵我玩，當正我係佢地屋企人咁。依家呢？人就搬咗，取而代之係岩岩搬入嚟嘅陌生人。每逢星期六日，我地都會翻教會做崇拜（唔開名），對於當時嘅小朋友嚟講幾張紙同膠紙已經夠佢地呢一場&ldquo;劍槍大戰&rdquo;，更不提某些老掉牙嘅團體遊戲。而隨著GameBoy嘅普及，我地嘅活動開始被電子產品侵蝕。但無可否認，牧場上的收割丶訓練員間的格鬥丶無間斷Chok嘅暴龍機丶他媽哥池陪伴了我多個歲月。「聽日一定會更開心姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪阿哈姆太郎？」每一個晚上，傻傻的少年睡前都會記起這句說話，不知不覺便睡著。然而，他仍相信這個說話，直到他睡醒。"},{"pid":"48cc8bbcb2f3a8015abc56889385b4600b5bac05","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T17:41:56.000Z","msg":"Sorry For 1999<br />\n第一次開Post 明白自己講得好唔順暢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎大家分享下自己嘅童年回憶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9c8a9322f7ce4c260623a0bc2203bc8868cb80","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T17:42:44.000Z","msg":"[quote]Sorry For 1999<br />\n第一次開Post 明白自己講得好唔順暢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎大家分享下自己嘅童年回憶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6bca5e72dcf089353e18088cf0b402dc3dd057","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T17:55:36.000Z","msg":"然後講起童年，點少得幼稚園小學時嘅小小小夫妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲記得當時大家對性都沒有很大概念<br />\n因此男女生都不會對任何異性接觸有尷尬<br />\n她係個喊包，咩事都可以喊一餐<br />\n而我係個好鍾意笑嘅人（至少細個係），笑對當時嘅我黎講係種必需品<br />\n機緣巧合地我地相識左，互叫對方老公仔老婆仔，仲互相應承對方父母大個左結婚。雖然只係對愛情毫無認識嘅小朋友之間兒戲嘅&ldquo;過家家&rdquo;，但係對於我黎講係一段揮之不去嘅回憶"},{"pid":"0312f5c11f3671891f9a20031aa6b462802a1480","tid":397782,"uid":144379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfad28ab4ec7bc038d2689b99851504f375fd62d","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc2bfdf5fc56e6286740c067cae46249937052f","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a76d7b5ab025f03526e9225c0069c887edd2a79","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe9932c95b04e1cc5d7ceabe34ff08373eadfe4","tid":397782,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote]Sorry For 1999<br />\n第一次開Post 明白自己講得好唔順暢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎大家分享下自己嘅童年回憶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3794ce83a5aa49b2d8637c30901b3fae17ee8d","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ded5bd77ff558a9cbd2