意佢<br />\n之後就冇再同過佢接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然小四完咗就冇接觸過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed9344786f7798b22121fc73470f47f1551f3ef","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T05:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幼稚園同班男仔爭住做一個女仔個老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小學仲係同班<br />\n鍾意佢去到小學畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小四同佢好fd<br />\n小五有個fd同佢講我鍾意佢<br />\n之後就冇再同過佢接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然小四完咗就冇接觸過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個Fd正HiHi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲野要本人親自講先夠誠意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔緊要啦 過去都已經過去左 仲有新嘅等住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e225d0a78b64f73ce36bf06b319675ac11711044","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cca31962e8c2a6c39a60559b3cff359c826cdae","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a983dc6bc2fbba3403ab0b6c61b4d6fdbd82a6e8","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0309844c509e427b0347f46910ddb083f1b5959a","tid":397782,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji